commit.message:
Add tokenizer for German language

The tokenizer is based on the existing Tokenizer for English. It adds
`-` and `.` to the valid characters list.

The client takes care of the filters itself.

Co-authored-by: Philipp Hahn <pmhahn+github@pmhahn.de>
Bump black and run it on enchant/_enchant.py
Update Apple Silicon installation in install.rst
